WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:32.540 --> 00:00:38.800
When processed correctly, a pile of soil
can be turned into an exquisite artwork.

00:01:03.620 --> 00:01:08.340
Chinaware, cí qì, is a part of daily life
in China.

00:01:09.260 --> 00:01:13.140
The surfaces are decorated with various exquisite patterns.

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:43.380
Some are as thin as paper; some are as
white as jade;

00:01:45.060 --> 00:01:47.360
some are as course as pottery;

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:51.680
and some are as black as lacquer.

00:01:54.700 --> 00:01:59.760
This is an extraordinary piece of blue
and white porcelain made in the 14th century.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:06.600
It was auctioned at more than 20
million pounds. It is the pride of cí qì.

00:02:13.400 --> 00:02:16.680
Cí qì is still called China in English

